KeysToEntries.story_5_1_000:
This is
our first time meeting…
but I’ve heard the rumors…
KeysToEntries.story_5_1_001:
I’m Takumi Fujiwara…
nice to meet you…
KeysToEntries.story_5_1_002:
I wasn’t planning
on battling in Akina
anymore…
KeysToEntries.story_5_1_003:
But since he asked me…
and because I decided
never to run away from a battle…
KeysToEntries.story_5_1_004:
Chasing my dream…
I’ll tear down Akina
at full speed‼
KeysToEntries.story_5_1_005:
Alright then…
let’s get this started…
